    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would serve well as a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical wear. The exterior shows noticeable scratches, a few small dents, and fading paint on the roof, while the interior has visible staining and some wear on the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it may require some suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to maintain its performance. It is a solid, functional car for its age, offered at a price that reflects its current state.",
