      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle exemplifies unrivaled preservation, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains indistinguishable from its original manufacture. Meticulously curated and mechanically peerless, this asset represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands an investment-grade vehicle of the highest caliber.",
      "price": 44500.0,
